title: Mark Normand
itunes:title: Mark Normand
description: My HoneyDew this week is Mark Normand! Mark shares some stories of childhood trauma including a home invasion where his parents were tied up and held hostage, a bed wetting phase, and the time he shit himself on a field trip. Mark talks about a different kind of back door incident that also did not go so well for him and his dream gig opening for Seinfeld and how he screwed it up big time. It’s another Dewzie!
